Former Big Brother Naija housemate, Khloe Abiri, has warned her fans against taking videos of her in public without her consent. The BBN star disclosed this in a video posted on social media, expressing that she would destroy anyone’s phone who is caught taking her videos in the public. She said, “You seeing someone outside and pull out your phone to make videos of their body. I am saying this publicly now, the next person I don’t care who you are, mother, father, aunty, anybody, friends, family, if you pull out your phone to record a video of me, I will break your phone. -Advertisement- “Trust me, I will not buy you any other phone and I have the right. You heard me. Do not bring out your phone especially if you are not a blogger.”